Translate Text (eng) To Speech (french)📝📻✨ 
Jupyter, Python, IBM Watson, IA, Huggingface 🤗

This app combines differents Steps:
*Input your text.
*It translates automatically to a chosen language.
*It generate a text file in your computer 📝.
*Finally, using the generated text file, It creates an audio file with a humanized voice in your desired language 🗣.
